      <title>戴森将在英国裁员约 1000 人，新任首席执行官将评估战略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/dyson-to-cut-about-1-000-uk-jobs-as-new-ceo-reviews-strategy</link>
